クラス Project

Object
Project
public class Project
extends Object
Model for project data. This contains some links data and files data.

      startDate - start-date of this project

      name - The name of this project
      overview - Overview of this project
      memo - Memo about this project
      linkList - List of links about this project
      fileLinkList - List of files about this project
